{"tid":2370197,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"猶太人喜歡鬥智計算 幾代打麻雀","createTime":"2021-01-17T23:25:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T00:04:21.000Z","uid":383344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"34a097e1d93f64db50e0bd3afab381752d5551e7","tid":2370197,"uid":383344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T23:25:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/culture/20210117/J2ESHNBGEBHF7FEZ36NIZGSB3Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fculture%2F20210117%2FJ2ESHNBGEBHF7FEZ36NIZGSB3Y%2F&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS1xDM7DnHmdvX2f5RcY9ddA%3D&h=17364c5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fculture%2F20210117%2FJ2ESHNBGEBHF7FEZ36NIZGSB3Y%2F&h=186e1cd9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/culture/20210117/J2ESHNBGEBHF7FEZ36NIZGSB3Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n猶太人精打細算　視為親子活動<br />\n<br />\n另一位做古董的朋友，就拿出了一副陳年在美國買的二十年代波士頓出品紙麻雀出來說歷史，上面竟然寫着麻雀是「最主導的中國遊戲」（The leading Chinese game）。住了紐約十多年的她說，美國猶太女人特別愛打中國麻雀，歐洲女人就愛打撲克，美國猶太人還會視打麻雀為親子活動，由細打到入老人院。「其實猶太人精打細算，可能是他們都愛鬥智計算的遊戲，我認識的猶太朋友幾代都會打麻雀。」<br />\n<br />\n網海打撈，見學者Gregg Swain早幾年花了五年時間鑽研猶太的麻雀文化，發現全美<strong>經常打麻雀的猶太人超過五十萬。</strong>世紀疫症期間數字或許會暴升，難怪引發有人量產摩登版本應市。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />叫雞胡 英文典講"},{"pid":"a4811db15991dd78bd53e7bc13470526b638efa9","tid":2370197,"uid":238920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T23:49:31.000Z","msg":"我淨係知索子英文叫bamboo<br />\n係個外國人黎香港exchange同我地講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b50017ec9fc09df8cd0cc7322e167cac8e0bb18e","tid":2370197,"uid":123020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T23:56:35.000Z","msg":"猶太人佢地果種麻雀都好食腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ade430009d6a925003ea1d7eadb1eff33a8966","tid":2370197,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T23:57:4